pageContext.claim: “O'Rourke voted against the border wall, oh, that's a good thing to -- he voted against Kate's law. And he voted for Obama amnesty, amnesty, Obama amnesty. O'Rourke even voted to shield MS-13 gang members from deportation. He doesn't want to deport them. He says they're people.”
pageContext.analysis: O'Rourke may differ with Trump on immigration policy, but there's no evidence that O'Rourke voted to protect MS-13 gang members from deportation.
